if anything happens.

22
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,590
Go!

23
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:16,510
Open the door.

24
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,680
Get in the car in an orderly manner.

25
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:21,210
Come on.

26
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,430
Careful.

27
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:25,840
Come.

28
