43
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,340
He will be in a coma for a while.

44
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,200
Even if you want to leave,

45
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,800
you should wait until the snow melts.

46
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,800
In snowy weather,

47
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,960
