48
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:26,920
I'm leaving.

49
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,930
You keep complaining that I lie to you.

50
00:05:57,430 --> 00:06:00,160
But you are the most gullible person
in the world.

51
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,750
Before I even spun a web,

52
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,830
you dove right in,

53
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,650
and I couldn't even drive you away.

54
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,680
Dad, Mom.

55
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,270
Xiaolan.

56
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,120
I have long been trapped in the dark,

57
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:22,110
and I'm used to moving alone.

58
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,720
But now, surprisingly,

59
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,970
