I am...

62
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,250
His sister-in-law.

63
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,630
The patient won't wake up for a while.

64
00:06:57,630 --> 00:06:59,430
You can go back and pack up first.

65
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,120
Take care of the wound
on your shoulder too.

66
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,450
Keep it away from water.

67
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,160
Qingyu.

68
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,720
The Huo family incident this time

69
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,180
involves too many people.

70
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,680
Someone will definitely
try to cause trouble.

71
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,310
So we have to trouble Ms. Ye and keep her

72
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:32,470
at the police station for a few more days.

73
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:34,070
I will take good care of them.

74
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:36,920
Alright.

75
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,750
I'll leave this matter

76
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:39,830
in your hands.

77
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:41,510
If you encounter any difficulties,

78
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:42,440
just let me know.

79
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:43,480
Understood.

80
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:50,650
Brother.

81
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:57,590
[File]

82
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,000
This is...

83
