86
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,930
What do you mean?

87
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,510
Some of the Huo family's subordinates said

88
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:17,510
the reason why sister-in-law
appeared in the vault

89
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,430
