outside the vault alone.

90
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:20,270
She was noticed

91
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,930
and accidentally dragged in.

92
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,000
Sister-in-law has long

93
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:31,080
had her eyes on
the Huo family's trafficking of orphans.

94
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,840
Okay.

95
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:45,870
I got it.

96
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:47,760
Go back to your work.

97
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,080
By the way.

98
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,270
Boze.

99
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,020
About this matter,

100
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,950
it's best not to let a third person know.

101
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,800
Don't worry, Qingyu.

102
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,870
When have I ever let you down?

103
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:15,960
[File]

104
00:09:16,060 --> 00:09:18,510
[Hong Fang Bank raided at night]

105
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,670
Are you reading

106
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,130
news on the Hong Fang Bank?

107
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:41,960
You're here.

108
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,720
You seem to

109
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:49,880
