120
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,630
yet you still have the mood
to talk in riddles with me here.

121
00:10:23,630 --> 00:10:26,360
You ought to seek justice
for him sooner instead.

122
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,630
The police

123
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,520
have intervened in this matter.

124
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:35,510
It's not convenient for
the Murong family to come forward.

125
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:36,390
Boze is

126
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,990
always fair in doing things.

127
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,560
There will be results soon.

128
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:45,600
I hope so.

129
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:47,610
I'm a little tired.

130
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,000
I'd like to rest now.

131
00:11:16,490 --> 00:11:18,920
[Hong Fang Bank]

132
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,840
Pay back! Pay back! Pay back!

133
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,240
Did something happen to the Huo family?

134
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,840
We all saw the police coming.

135
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,600
Won't anyone give
the depositors an explanation?

136
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,200
Quiet, everyone!

137
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,120
Quiet, quiet!

138
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,600
Quiet, everyone.

139
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,480
Listen to me.

140
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,480
Hong Fang Bank
is a long-established brand,

141
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,080
