146
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:39,240
Trust me, okay?

147
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,630
Words are cheap!

148
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,750
Why should we believe you?

149
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,720
We just want our money!

150
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,250
Pay back!

151
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,150
Give me the money!

152
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:44,870
No, wait.

153
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:45,910
Calm down.

154
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:47,150
Calm down, calm down!

155
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:49,270
-Calm down. Calm down.
-Pay us back!

156
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,790
Pay us back! Pay us back!

157
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:51,420
What are you doing?

158
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,420
Pay us back!

159
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,270
What are you doing?

160
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,800
What are you doing?

161
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,600
What are you doing?

162
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,660
What are you doing?

163
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:57,670
It's perfectly justified

164
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,790
to demand a debt payment,

165
00:11:58,790 --> 00:11:59,960
am I right?

166
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:02,670
Pay us back! Pay us back!

167
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:04,270
-Pay us back!
-It’s him! Take him away!

168
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,360
-Stop it!
-Take him away.

169
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:06,740
[Huo Residence]

170
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:11,240
I left the bank in your care

171
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,750
because you were reliable.

172
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:16,890
Now that such a big mistake has occurred,

173
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,480
what do you have to say for yourself?

174
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,280
Young Master.

175
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,510
The vault operations
had always been secretive

176
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,270
and heavily guarded.

177
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:22,480
Nothing had ever gone wrong before.

178
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,200
Besides,

179
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:23,870
in Nancheng,

180
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:25,930
no one dared to target our Huo family.

181
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,440
I just really didn't expect
that Murong Qing...

182
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,120
Trash!

183
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,630
Brainless fool!

184
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,870
Brainless fool!

185
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,840
You kidnapped Murong Qingyu's fiancée

186
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,840
