187
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:36,770
And you expected
the Murong family not to retaliate?

188
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:37,790
No, Young Master...

189
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:39,030
-I think you’ve become too complacent
-Young Master.

190
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,360
as the manager, haven't you?

191
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:40,960
Haven't you?

192
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:41,690
Haven't you?

193
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,050
-Haven't you?
-Enough.

194
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:47,720
Why are you yelling at your elder?

195
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,390
Master.

196
00:12:58,670 --> 00:12:59,630
Please, for the sake of my many years

197
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:01,240
of loyalty and hard work
for the Huo family,

198
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,270
spare my life.

199
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:03,510
I was at fault this time.

200
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:04,390
It was my mistake.

201
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:05,440
I didn't manage the vault well.

202
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:05,910
Master.

203
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:07,570
Please spare my life, Master.

204
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,510
Over the years,

205
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,580
I believe I have treated you well.

206
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,270
Ma... Master.

207
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:25,150
Master.

208
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:28,120
For making such a huge mistake,

209
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,720
breaking both your arms

210
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,180
isn't going too far, is it?

211
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:34,440
Master...

212
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:35,200
Master!

213
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:35,900
Master!

214
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:36,460
Master!

215
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,030
Master!

216
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:37,960
Please spare my life!

217
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,630
Master!

218
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:40,750
For the sake of my many years of service,

219
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,950
please spare my life!

220
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,720
Master!

221
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:43,720
Master!

222
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:47,630
Grandfather.

223
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:48,960
Don't be angry.

224
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,210
It's a small matter.

225
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:51,860
Have a seat.

226
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:57,840
Grandfather.

227
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:00,200
Right now at the bank,

228
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,320
depositors are causing a run,

229
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,870
and major clients are withdrawing funds.

230
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:04,270
What should we do next?

231
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:07,000
The lifeblood of the Huo family

232
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,130
is not just the bank.

233
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:11,470
As long as the South
still needs our imported arms,

234
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,320
the Huo family won't fall.

235
00:14:18,670 --> 00:14:19,930
What do you want to say?

236
00:14:20,870 --> 00:14:21,670
Grandfather.

237
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:23,910
I...

238
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,440
I previously embezzled
some funds from the South

239
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:28,030
and put it in the stock market.

240
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:30,030
I thought it was a sure-fire profit.

241
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,180
Unexpectedly,

242
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,480
I lost it all.

243
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,910
You bastard!

244
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,390
How dare you embezzle the money

245
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,550
and lose it all?

246
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:42,550
Are you trying to ruin the Huo family?

247
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:43,600
Do you know that

248
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,080
once the arms supply
to the south is cut off,

249
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,280
our Huo family will really be finished?

250
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,190
Grandfather,

251
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:49,870
I was wrong.

252
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,720
I know I was wrong.

253
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,450
I will never dare to do it again.

254
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:53,840
Please tell me

255
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:55,010
what to do next.

256
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:00,600
It seems

257
00:15:02,390 --> 00:15:04,320
we can only go to that family now.

258
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,600
Who?

259
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,750
Nanny Sun's case

260
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,790
has been classified as a missing case,

261
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:25,190
and temporarily closed.

262
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:28,310
The most troublesome one is Murong Qingyu.

263
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:29,960
You just said that

264
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,840
he's suspecting you now?

265
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,000
He seems to know

266
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:36,840
about my early involvement

267
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,170
with the Hong Fang Bank.

268
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:40,080
How did he know?

269
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:43,200
Maybe Li Boze suspects me.

270
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,360
But he doesn't have much evidence.

271
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:48,420
At least he hasn't found out
about my real identity yet.

272
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,720
Li Boze and I have crossed paths

273
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:52,270
several times.

274
00:15:53,270 --> 00:15:55,240
He is also suspicious of me.

275
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,960
You caused a scene at the vault.

276
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,820
I'm afraid the Huo family
is already targeting you.

277
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:09,120
Going head-to-head with the Huo family...

278
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,910
Isn't that what we want?

279
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,200
I didn't expect you

280
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:26,590
to have such a history with them.

281
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:28,720
Their old master and I

282
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,930
did great things together back then.

283
00:16:31,270 --> 00:16:33,750
They wouldn't dare stand by
and watch us go down.

284
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:35,010
I'll leave this matter

285
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:36,240
to you.

286
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:37,320
Okay.

287
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,120
